Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory730.jpg'}
{3: 'Stopping before the stage, you turn around to speak to Bambinata, only to feel a slight bump behind you.'}
{1: '1', 3: 'You turn to find Bambinata crashing into you, unable to stop in time.'}
{2: 'Bambinata?'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: '...Is it time to stop?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: 'Ugh... Did Bambinata do something wrong again?', 4: '1'}
{2: "You didn't do anything wrong. You did well.", 3: '10'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: "You don't seem upset, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: "Because you didn't do anything wrong.", 3: '13'}
{3: 'Her confused blue eyes turn to look at you, only relaxing upon confirming that you are not angry.'}
{2: 'Do you like it here, Bambinata?', 3: '15'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: 'Bambinata will make every effort to fulfill your orders, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: 'But when Bambinata saw you in the maze...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: 'It felt... different.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: "Bambinata doesn't know how to describe it without any similar memories to reference.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: 'But Bambinata was... happy.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'She pauses before taking two steps toward you.'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: 'Do... you have any new orders, Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'What do you want to do now, Bambinata?', 3: '23'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: '...What does Bambinata want to do?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Standing on the stage in an awkward silence, she looks like a wind-up doll that has lost its clockwork.'}
{2: 'Do you want to dance?', 3: '26'}
{2: 'Bambinata', 3: 'D-dance...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Before she can "remember," Bambinata is already standing gracefully on her toes, ready to dance.'}
{3: 'Some things cannot be forgotten, even if her memories are wiped.'}
{3: 'The things that one likes... the people that one likes.'}
